-- Gamesa Holds Talks With Unions to Extend Job Layoffs for 7% of Workforce
-- B y   C h a r l e s   P e n t y
-- 2010-10-04T10:05:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/gamesa-holds-talks-with-unions-to-extend-job-layoffs-for-7-of-workforce.html
Gamesa Corporacion Tecnologica SA
will start talks with unions to extend temporary job cuts
affecting 309 Spanish workers, or 7 percent of its domestic
workforce, the company said in a filing to regulators today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Charles Penty at 
 cpenty@bloomberg.net  